Turn left and walk across the room to face the back of the toilet.
Place the soap on the back of the toilet.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the right side of the sink.
Pick up the soap in the cabinet under the left side of the right sink.
Turn left and walk across the room to face the back of the toilet.
Place the bar of soap on the back of the toilet.

Place the soap on top of the toilet tank.

Take out the soap from the left cupboard underneath the sink.
Turn around and move toward the toilet on the opposite corner of the room.
Place the soap next to the other soap on top of the toilet tank.
anns.task_desc: Organize the bars of soap on top of the toilet tank.
